CMake Qt6 Quick Template
------------------------

You need Qt6 and CMake 3.16 or higher

-- Build instructions --

cd /home/Salman/projects/crs-dso
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ../
make

src/crs-dso


-- Tutorials and resources --

Qt online docs
https://doc.qt.io/


  Running the Program

  Development Build (using presets)

  cd /home/Salman/projects/crs-dso
  cmake --preset default
  cmake --build --preset default
  ./build/src/crs-dso

  Manual Build

  cd /home/Salman/projects/crs-dso
  mkdir build && cd build
  cmake ../
  make
  ./src/crs-dso

  Release Build

  cmake --preset release
  cmake --build --preset release
  ./build-release/src/crs-dso

  ---
  Cross-Platform Builds

  Since this is a Qt6 application, you'll need to use Qt's deployment tools to create standalone builds:

  Linux

  cmake --preset release && cmake --build --preset release
  # Use linuxdeployqt (install from https://github.com/probonopd/linuxdeployqt)
  linuxdeployqt build-release/src/crs-dso -qmldir=src/qml -appimage

  Windows

  cmake --preset release
  cmake --build --preset release
  windeployqt --qmldir src\qml build-release\src\crs-dso.exe

  macOS

  cmake --preset release
  cmake --build --preset release
  macdeployqt build-release/src/crs-dso.app -qmldir=src/qml -dmg

  ---
  Requirements

  - Qt 6.5+ with Quick and Charts modules
  - CMake 3.16+
  - Ninja (used by the presets) or Make

  The project currently doesn't have deployment scripts, so you may want to create platform-specific build scripts if you frequently build for distribution.
